Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:19.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:23.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我心雀跃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:28.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}现在与你一起飞奔而出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:31.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:37.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}跟随内心的声音前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向着让自己雀跃不已的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:46.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}时间变得仿佛就如梦境一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:52.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但是想要找到那份独一无二的真实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在你眼眸深处的…
